# ── Original third_party files we DON'T need ──
# Keep only what our CMake build uses:
#   freetype, zlib, agg23, lcms, libopenjpeg, libjpeg_turbo (no asm/simd), fast_float, abseil-cpp (headers only, no tests), icu (headers only, no data), harfbuzz (no perf/test)
# Exclude everything else:
/third_party/abseil-cpp/*.def
/third_party/abseil-cpp/absl/**/testdata/
